features: 【Adorable Farmhouse Decor】This is a vintage styled glass vase with 4 Pcs greenery, also a beautiful accent jar lantern with removable florals, so this piece can be used throughout the year. Perfect for home decor and floral arrangements

【Versatile Function】Rustic vase with lush greenery works with your unique decorating style! Fits in perfectly with most any home decor style, Farmhouse, Rustic, Lakeside, Industrial or Boho chic in your Bedroom, living room, kitchen or dining room

【Perfect Size】Approx 11.8" tall, measuring from the bottom of the vase to the top of the greenery. The vintage farmhouse lantern is about 6.3"width x 6.3" height, and is sure to add a warm ambience any room

【Rustic Jar Vase】The vintage styled glass lantern vase has a clear glass jar encased in a rustic brown metal frame. It is filled with faux plant branches that look and feel real, perfectly fit for farmhouse style decorating

【Ideal Room Decor】Beautiful glass and metal container with handle to use as a flower vase or candle holder. The piece with a light string is sure to light up that space that you have been looking for "just the right thing" for
body.description: Featuring heavy craft glass vase with a unique, rustic metal frame & wire surround including a metal handle for hanging if you wish! You will love the large size, sturdiness and uniqueness of this gorgeous vase! Just add the bouquets we have to offer, or incorporate the piece with just other simple pretty candle or greenery you have!See more info about the glass lantern vase below:-- This piece measures approximately 11.8" tall with the lush greenery branches.-- Greenery is plastic but not fake or cheesy looking.-- Add sand, pebbles, shells, colored rocks, etc. to the vase for an even more unique look! Or add water to make the bouquet look "alive"! There are so many ways to display this pretty vase as you wish!-- Jar Vase by itself dimensions:---- Full Diameter: 6.9"---- Height: 6.3"-- Information on lights:---- The 3-mode light string is a small addition to the gorgeous piece and will require button battery replacement!---- Lights last approximately 40- 60hrs with intermittent use.---- You will need a small screwdriver to replace the batteries.If you love farmhouse style decorating this vintage piece is perfect for you. Rustic glass metal vase can is filled with high quality artificial plants that are secured in plastic. This will add a farmhouse touch to any room in your home. Accented with the simple rubiginous metal frame and look as if the plants are growing out of the glass jar.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this!
reviews.reviewText: I love this .. it’s so simple yet adds just the right touch. The only thing I’d change is the greenery. What I received was pretty short/small and looked as if it were just leftovers from others that had been put together. I will purchase some greenery elsewhere to get the fuller look instead of left overs. Otherwise I love it. The lights will be easy to replace if I should ever need to. They just lay loosely inside the jar. This could also be done a little nicer with something for it the lights to rest on but it’s still a great purchase and I’d buy it again.
